Chairman.

44
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:49,559
Hello, Chairman. My name is Lin Huai-en. I'm from the marketing team.

45
00:02:49,559 --> 00:02:52,260
May I take a few minutes of your time?

46
00:02:58,860 --> 00:03:00,020
Yes?

47
00:03:00,020 --> 00:03:03,400
Chairman, it's good to finally see you.

48
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:06,320
Ever since the first day I've worked here,

49
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:09,520
I've wanted to visit you and the late Chairman.

50
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,159
Did you know my father?

51
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:14,320
I grew up in Rende Orphanage, sponsored by Poseidon Department Store.

52
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:16,380
I've always dreamed of working here,

53
