so that I can repay your kindness.

54
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,299
I see.

55
00:03:22,299 --> 00:03:24,280
The orphanage director,

56
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:28,160
children at the orphanage and I

57
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,700
are very sorry

58
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:33,650
that the late Chairman has passed away.

59
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:35,760
Sorry for your loss.

60
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:40,480
Thank you for your concern.

61
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:42,389
Thank you very much.

62
00:03:42,389 --> 00:03:45,309
