64
00:03:47,519 --> 00:03:52,430
You're welcome. Poseidon Department Store always cares about those in need.

65
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:56,489
I will continue my father's custom from now on.

66
00:03:56,490 --> 00:04:00,220
