72
00:04:19,509 --> 00:04:21,400
Do you know Dai Zhe-ni?

73
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:24,760
Yes. Chairman, how did you know?

74
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:29,550
Anyway, if you see him, tell him that—

75
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,939
Never mind. It's okay.

76
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,810
Thank you Chairman.

77
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,710
[Missed call]

78
00:04:41,650 --> 00:04:45,550
Is Hai Yi really angry with me and ignoring me?

79
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:52,690
Dai Zhe-ni. I just bumped into the chairman.

80
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:55,039
Really? Did he ask about me?

81
00:04:55,039 --> 00:04:56,080
