144
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:07,390
Three days. You'll have it in three days.

145
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:10,700
"Three days"? Are you brushing me off?

146
00:09:12,370 --> 00:09:17,790
Chairman, I'm always conscientious and dedicated to work.

147
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:21,010
Is there any misunderstanding?

148
00:09:21,010 --> 00:09:24,000
