149
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,240
Does it sound like a misunderstanding?

150
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:30,310
Regarding this, I'm working with the relevant departments on strategies.

151
00:09:30,310 --> 00:09:34,890
I hope that Managing Director Liang can tell me your strategies,

152
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:38,250
before Poseidon Department Store is shut down,

153
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:40,680
or it is acquired by Luquan Group.

154
00:09:41,430 --> 00:09:46,390
Chairman, are you questioning my ability,

155
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:48,699
or my loyalty to the company?

156
00:09:48,699 --> 00:09:50,530
What do you think?

157
00:09:51,530 --> 00:09:55,080
Our late Chairman never had doubts about me.

158
00:09:56,080 --> 00:10:00,850
A new chief brings in new aides.

159
00:10:11,490 --> 00:10:14,120
Hello? Vice Chairman Wu.

160
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:17,380
I just saw Hai Yi lecturing Liang Wun-sen.

161
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:19,440
He's not happy with him.

162
00:10:41,730 --> 00:10:45,740
Congratulations, Zhe-ni.

163
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:47,820
The Chairman has just assigned you

164
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:50,420
to be his executive assistant.

165
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:51,849
Really?

166
00:10:51,850 --> 00:10:55,690
Of course. The official appointment has been announced.

167
00:10:56,940 --> 00:10:59,560
Yes! Hai Yi still needs me.

168
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,950
That's awesome!

169
00:11:01,950 --> 00:11:05,159
Wait. According to what Momo taught me,

170
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:07,410
I can't say yes immediately.

171
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:12,860
Director, I'd like to stay a bit longer in the customer service team.

172
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:14,959
I don't want to be transferred to another department.

173
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,500
It's not just any department.

174
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:18,790
You'll be the executive assistant to the chairman.

175
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:21,410
It's a dream job.

176
00:11:21,410 --> 00:11:24,069
Working here for Poseidon Department Store

177
00:11:24,069 --> 00:11:25,809
is also a way to serve Chairman.

178
00:11:25,809 --> 00:11:27,640
It's the same.

179
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:38,710
Dai Zhe-ni will be very happy when he hears the news.

180
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:42,680
What should I say to him first when I see him later?

181
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:50,079
Should I act as if nothing has happened?

182
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:53,110
Or...

183
00:11:54,310 --> 00:11:56,509
Should I give him a hug?

184
00:11:56,510 --> 00:11:59,200
That seems a bit much.

185
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,430
Come in.

186
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:10,569
Chairman.

187
00:12:10,570 --> 00:12:16,210
The *HR team said Dai Zhe-ni didn't accept the job transfer.
(*human resources)

188
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:20,890
All right. I understand.

189
00:12:43,590 --> 00:12:45,460
Lin Huai-en.

190
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:47,999
- What brings you here?
- I have to take this to your manager.

191
00:12:47,999 --> 00:12:51,060
He's not in the office. Leave it to me. I'll pass it onto him.

192
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:53,350
Sure. Thanks.

193
00:12:55,350 --> 00:12:57,349
Have you made up with Chairman?

194
00:12:57,349 --> 00:12:58,600
That is troubling me.

195
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,689
What happened?

196
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:01,879
They say Chairman made you his executive assistant.

197
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:03,910
I turned it down.

198
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,109
Why?

199
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:08,330
We shouldn't talk about it here. Shall we go for a drink tonight?

200
00:13:08,330 --> 00:13:11,549
I can't. I have to take my friend's shift.

201
00:13:11,549 --> 00:13:13,339
I don't think so.

202
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:15,549
You are going on a date with Managing Director.

203
00:13:15,549 --> 00:13:18,989
Of course not. Don't say that.

204
00:13:18,989 --> 00:13:20,459
Never mind.

205
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:23,920
Someone forgets about his friend when he's in love.

206
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:38,659
- Managing Director Liang.
- Yes.

207
00:13:38,659 --> 00:13:41,329
I know you love Japanese cuisine.

208
00:13:41,329 --> 00:13:45,100
This is one of my favorite places. Try it.

209
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:46,949
Vice Chairman Wu, you don't have to do this.

210
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:50,670
Here. If you recommend it, it must be the best.

211
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:53,110
Good.

212
00:13:53,110 --> 00:13:56,910
I'll treat you as one of us and just say it directly.

213
00:13:56,910 --> 00:14:00,680
All the board members would like you to be the chairman.

214
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:04,780
Hai Yang just favored his own son.

215
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:10,510
But... it's human nature.

216
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:15,250
I heard that you rejected the daughter of Luquan Group.

217
00:14:16,780 --> 00:14:20,550
Vice Chairman Wu, you certainly have your sources.

218
00:14:23,890 --> 00:14:27,780
You made Ms. Lu very angry.

219
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:30,919
Why did you reject such a great opportunity?

220
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:33,940
Don't you want to take this chance to advance?

221
00:14:35,060 --> 00:14:36,910
As a matter of fact,

222
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:39,059
I don't have to be with Lu Si-chi,

223
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:43,460
I can achieve what I want with my own ability.

224
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:47,310
All right. I love your confidence.

225
00:14:47,310 --> 00:14:48,809
Thank you, Vice Chairman Wu.

226
00:14:48,810 --> 00:14:54,329
But I have a plan to make it happen within a month.

227
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:57,060
Are you interested in hearing it?

228
00:15:00,890 --> 00:15:02,970
