229
00:15:02,970 --> 00:15:04,619
Hello. Here are your meals.

230
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:08,260
"*Only an outstanding talent can recognize current trends."
(*anticipate what is happening)

231
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:12,390
I can't wait to see Hai Yi's face

232
00:15:12,390 --> 00:15:14,410
when you're the chairman in a month.

233
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:17,310
- Come on. Cheers.
- Cheers.

234
00:15:31,130 --> 00:15:34,710
Managing Director, what are you scheming with Vice Chairman Wu?

235
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:37,820
He said you would be Chairman within a month. What does that mean?

236
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:40,740
Why are you here? Are you working here?

237
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:43,240
I'm just substituting for a friend tonight.

238
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:46,790
It's not a secret part-time job. But you...

239
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:49,630
How could you have no conscience at all?

240
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:52,149
The company situation is a bit complicated now,

241
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:55,039
but I can't tell you all the details.

242
00:15:55,039 --> 00:15:57,219
Anyway, colluding with Vice Chairman Wu

243
00:15:57,220 --> 00:16:01,220
and abandoning the Poseidon Department Store, which has trained you over the years, are so wrong.

244
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:02,459
Huai-en, it's really not—

245
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:05,190
I saw it and heard it clearly.

246
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:07,600
I didn't know you were this kind of person.

247
00:16:14,350 --> 00:16:16,960
I'm sorry for letting you down.

248
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:22,000
This is business and there are rules.

249
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:26,219
Please believe me.

250
00:16:26,220 --> 00:16:29,970
I won't hurt you no matter what I do.

251
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:37,340
You are hurting me if you hurt Chairman.

252
00:16:58,990 --> 00:17:00,949
He has time to spend at the gym,

253
00:17:00,950 --> 00:17:04,890
but he has no time to text me or call me?

254
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:19,150
He obviously saw me. Why didn't he say hi to me?

255
00:17:19,150 --> 00:17:21,370
Is he ignoring me?

256
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:25,660
Coach, please tell that guy

