00:18:34,890 --> 00:18:37,179
not to think that other people can't do it if he can't.

261
00:18:37,179 --> 00:18:39,240
Who's embarrassing?

262
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:42,829
Coach, please tell the guy in the backless top that

263
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:45,599
it's someone else's turn to use the equipment now.

264
00:18:45,599 --> 00:18:49,000
Coach, I'm a VVIP customer here.

265
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:53,320
I'm a bit in the way. You two can talk directly.

266
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:21,260
Huai-en, why didn't you come in?

267
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:24,820
I have something to say to you, and I'll go once I'm done.

268
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:27,769
Is it about last night?

269
00:19:27,769 --> 00:19:31,070
