272
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:42,529
He's young, lacks experience and is arrogant.

273
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:44,790
How can I help him?

274
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:49,490
None of the board members is willing to entrust the company to him.

275
00:19:49,490 --> 00:19:53,299
Anyway... I believe in Chairman.

276
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:57,200
Give him some time and he'll be a good leader.

277
00:19:58,550 --> 00:20:01,320
I'm the reason why the company has had

278
00:20:01,320 --> 00:20:03,650
a good performance over the last few years.

279
00:20:03,650 --> 00:20:07,470
Everyone knows it, right?

280
00:20:08,260 --> 00:20:10,259
I didn't expect you to be so ambitious,

281
00:20:10,259 --> 00:20:12,620
