282
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:14,950
You really disappoint me.

283
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:38,520
♫ Listen, the phone is ringing ♫

284
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:41,780
♫ My reflex ♫

285
00:20:41,780 --> 00:20:45,900
♫ I think of you involuntarily ♫

286
00:20:45,900 --> 00:20:52,040
♫ I forgot that we are nothing ♫

287
00:20:52,040 --> 00:20:58,070
